{"tid":1569340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831後極可疑既'自殺'案件","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T08:33:26.000Z","uid":89006,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c13695a95f76f8affd649808afa092369a9a0046","tid":1569340,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Case  1 </span></strong> [/size=2]<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雙手綁繩連膠籃放磚頭 男子浮屍北角海面</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">7/9 星期六 早上8點被發現 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190907/60018940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60018940&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=a65dc8bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60018940&h=c63ee928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190907/60018940</a> (0907 08:56)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">蘋果： 死者姓鄭(81歲) ，警方在其住所內檢獲遺書，懷疑他因病厭世，<span style=\"color: red;\">經調查後相信無可疑</span>。 有市民發現，於是報警。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190907/bkn-20190907083246166-0907_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190907%2Fbkn-20190907083246166-0907_00822_001.html&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=c81798da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190907/bkn-20190907083246166-0907_00822_001.html</a> (09月07日(六)08:32建立) </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">東網：警方發現死者腰部纏有紅色繩及一個環保袋，內有4塊磚頭及一個膠籃，<span style=\"color: red;\">一度懷疑事件有可疑</span>。 2名男女親友到場認屍。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑點 </span> from</span> : <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1549796/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1549796/page/1</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Case  2 </span></strong> [/size=4]   <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>  理大校園男子墮樓身亡<span style=\"color: orange;\"></strong></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <br />\n7/9 星期六  晚上7:56 分左右<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190907/60021110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60021110&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=aa59ffb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60021110&h=f99aa605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190907/60021110</a> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">31歲  姓鍾  男 <br />\n 警員接獲報案， 一名男子暈倒在Z座南座地上 ，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現場未有發出巨響</span></strong>，懷疑先在樹上卸力墮地<br />\n- 身上只有香港專業教育學院學生證<span style=\"color: red;\"> ( 非理大學生或教職員)</span><br />\n- <strong>係 Z座11樓跳落</strong>（<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>疑點: 非poly人點上去？</strong></span></span><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1550167/page/11）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1550167/page/11）</a><br />\n- <ins>[orange]警方調查後表示死者有精神病記錄，認為事件沒有可疑。</span></ins><br />\n- 據 01 所稱： 有事主家人其後到場了解事件。</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/372795/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E9%9D%9E%E6%95%99%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F372795%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=05057c85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/372795/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E9%9D%9E%E6%95%99%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1</a> (2019-09-07 22:01)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ama53ps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fama53ps.jpg&h=b6c1cb03&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pH33QCC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpH33QCC.png&h=e1269316&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 無出入紀錄，又無CCTV</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有巴打話識死者, 稱唔關831同政治事，死者亦唔係poly舊生 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">from <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1550167/page/8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1550167/page/8</a>  (page 4, 12)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWAavbf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWAavbf.png&h=73226838&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Case  3 </span></strong> </span>  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">   男子失蹤3日 秀茂坪邨墮樓亡</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">11/9  星期三  早上11時24分接報<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Source: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190911/60033014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60033014&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=917ad02f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60033014&h=db7bcdeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190911/60033014</a></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">蘋果：23歲 朱植雄 男   無遺書，<ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">警員相信事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定</span></ins>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190911/bkn-20190911114101695-0911_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190911%2Fbkn-20190911114101695-0911_00822_001.html&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=2ecb454d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190911/bkn-20190911114101695-0911_00822_001.html</a> (09月11日(三) 11:41) </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">東網：<span style=\"color: red;\">有街坊發現一名男子昏迷倒臥在上址天井</span>，立即慌忙報警求助。經初步調查後，懷疑有情緒病記錄</span><br />\n<br />\n本周一(9號)上午離開<span style=\"color: orange;\">[size=4]秀茂坪秀明道</span></span>的住所後便告失蹤，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">三日後於秀茂坪邨秀義樓被發現倒卧在一樓天井位置</span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbrwY6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbrwY6S.png&h=d8a10a6a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有兩位巴打指死者位置對面有一條樓梯 ，而樓梯上邊有個巴士站<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">疑點 and 相 (請跳去Page 20同21) from  </span></strong></span><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1561987/page/21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1561987/page/21</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">14/9 有樓主話係死者親人</span>，由BB就開始識，表示死者唔係被自殺，一次發夢都無去，<span style=\"color: red;\">話有CCTV</span>。from <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1567462/page/16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1567462/page/16</a><br />\n佢話條CCTV係：<ins>差佬傳俾佢媽媽，佢媽媽傳俾我，有whatsapp紀錄</ins> (page 4 ）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KA2mkK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KA2mkK.png&h=e9643bfa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTV: </span></strong>[size=5] <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/359942485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F359942485&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e43a07f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/359942485</a> （Post 既 page 16）<br />\nCCTV (6秒片段) 顯示時間係2019年9月9日 - 09：54，而死者係係11號早上11點多被發現，</span><strong>[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">幾日都無人發現？ </span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">片中男子蓄短頭髮，身穿白色背心，紅色短褲同深色拖鞋。睇番10 號失蹤既新聞 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190910/60030936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60030936&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=5a46c621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60030936&h=c0c3c4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190910/60030936</a> - 蓄短黑髮，最後露面時身穿白色背心、紅色短褲及深色拖鞋。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTV 睇唔到樣，唔確定係咪同一個人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">樓主(自稱死者親人)話死者星期一(9號)朝已經跳左，到星期三(11號)先發現，有份認屍。</span><br />\nfrom <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1567462/page/16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1567462/page/16</a>  Page 17 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxjiD7J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxjiD7J.png&h=fe70c1f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑黑警hack左樓主account 再出post  </span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">因為樓主背景同死者朱植雄相似，post左一張身分證（朱植x，為死者名字）證明自己係親人，身高一樣，疑似住係秀茂坪，有情緒病 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569012/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569012/page/1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">14/9 有人話係死者朋友，另一個friend出事前一晚(10號)有同死者whatsapp</span></span></strong> <br />\nfrom <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1567247/page/26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1567247/page/26</a> ( Page 15尾 )</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZczWUy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZczWUy.png&h=5193e7de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMibZzM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMibZzM.png&h=8393bcb7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n死者並唔係住係秀義樓<br />\n到底附近有無人聽到巨響？<br />\n係天台跳落去，係咪會跌左落個個位到？<br />\n報案人係點發現到死者？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"34fa2e5c424e103f0176a175d1025d032476f8cb","tid":1569340,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你個臭街！<br />\n今日死差佬同藍絲又周圍打人呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n聽日九月十五日<br />\n<br />\n12pm 金鐘 英領<br />\n2pm 銅鑼灣東角道 /<br />\n維園  </span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全人類同我出黎！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔係我屌埋你老母呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/915/652/b49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F915%2F652%2Fb49.gif&h=c007be28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div></span>"},{"pid":"082110912039ccbd459d57b7c807058eb6ac01df","tid":1569340,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Case  4 </span></strong> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">     <span style=\"font-size: large;\">女子太和邨墮樓 送院搶救無效亡</span></span></strong><br />\n [size=2]12/9 星期四 01：51  <br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190912/bkn-20190912023308191-0912_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190912%2Fbkn-20190912023308191-0912_00822_001.html&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=70989256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190912/bkn-20190912023308191-0912_00822_001.html</a> (09月12日 四 02:33建立)</span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">64歲  姓蔡 女    現場有遺書，警員相信事件無可疑</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">疑點1<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇咁啱會有 5名便衣係附近仲要咁快到達現場？</span></strong><br />\n仲要當時已經係凌晨？<br />\n<br />\n疑點2<br />\n<strong>[size=3]<span style=\"color: red;\">附近嘅居民完全聽唔到有巨響</span></span></strong><br />\n相信有試過屋企附近有人跳樓一定會知<br />\n因為個下嘅聲係大到就算你訓緊教會嘈醒你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以上疑點 from <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1562791/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1562791/page/1</a></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2e32e6e1be6bf4a02c5da487358e59a31db75f6d","tid":1569340,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"狗隻肯定拎左死者電話黎用<br />\n用死人野<img src=\"